Reasoning: The paper deals with the performance analysis and compensation of IQ imbalance in a wireless communication system, which falls under the domain of information theory (cs.IT) and communication (cs.COMM). The use of STBC and OFDM techniques suggests that the paper may also belong to the sub-categories of systems and control (cs.SY) and networking and internet architecture (cs.NI). Finally, the proposed compensation algorithms involve signal processing techniques, which may also place the paper in the multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category.
